  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nSometimes there are high rate of rejected voluntary exit on mainnet\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1294\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-18 at 11 45 46\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/232673756-0c95e334-d562-46d4-8f0c-4ffc29dc022b.png\">\r\n\r\nthis happens more frequently on our test mainnet nodes\r\n\r\nRight now it's likely we don't use correct state to validate a voluntary exit https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/3ee1d8a5acb09160827b185c79d2ead80442c0e7/packages/beacon-node/src/chain/validation/voluntaryExit.ts#L25\r\n\r\nDue to that it may affect gossip score p4 params\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\n- Low rate or 0% rejected voluntary exits on mainnet\r\n- May use state at VoluntaryExit's epoch (may use a metric to see epoch difference against current epoch). Make sure it does not effect performance of our regen module\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n\r\n- Version: v1.7.2\r\n",
